    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving engine delivers exceptional throttle response via individual throttle bodies and is mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis maintains its composure through corners thanks to a factory-spec M-Variable Lock differential and a well-sorted suspension geometry. Mechanically sound, this E46 has had the VANOS system serviced and the rear subframe inspected for structural integrity, ensuring the torque is delivered reliably to the rear wheels. The exterior retains a clean aesthetic with minor road patina consistent with its age, while the interior remains a focused cockpit for the spirited driver. A mechanically honest example of a modern classic, optimized for tactile feedback and analog performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
